title: Finding the smallest quarter and spread.
body: A survey was conducted of $$130$$ purchasers of new BMW $$3$$ series cars, $$130$$ purchasers of new BMW $$5$$ series cars, and $$130$$ purchasers of new BMW $$7$$ series cars.
